Array-APX version 0.04
======================

Array::APX gives Perl some APL functionality. It provides the APX-class 
which includes basic APL-like operators and functions and overloads many
of the built-in operators with their APX-counterparts which become active
when applied to APX-objects.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Array::DeepUtils

